metadata.name: Le Rondini
metadata.description:
Taken late in the day near the town of Argostoli on the Greek island of Kefalonia in 2020.

Made with Kodak Professional Film and a Mamiya 7 medium format film camera. 

Scanned with a Noritsu HS-1800. Colour graded and edited specifically for digital use.

6000X5000px
